[{"ave_id":"AVE-2009-0016","file_name":"2009/AVE-2009-0016.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2009-5020","title":"AWStats awredir.pl 开放重定向漏洞","description":"AWStats 6.95 之前版本中的 awredir.pl 脚本存在开放重定向漏洞（CWE-20：输入验证不当）。远程攻击者可通过特制请求，利用该漏洞将用户重定向至任意恶意网站，进而实施钓鱼攻击窃取敏感信息。攻击者无需身份认证即可发起攻击，但需诱使用户点击恶意链接，CVSS 评分 5.8，危害等级中。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.8,"aliases":["CVE-2009-5020"],"sources":["cve","nuclei"],"published":"2010-12-02","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 AWStats 至 6.95 或更高版本以修复 awredir.pl 中的开放重定向漏洞。如无法升级，在 Web 服务器层面对 awredir.pl 脚本的访问添加 URL 白名单校验规则，限制重定向目标仅为受信任域名。同时检查 Web 日志中是否存在利用该漏洞的异常重定向请求。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://awstats.sourceforge.net/docs/awstats_changelog.txt","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2009/CVE-2009-5020.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2009/CVE-2009-5020.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/de9949dedbd4d7d071222d7c816d86aa68e1eb86/cves/2009/5xxx/CVE-2009-5020.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/f29605a96fd1261602d83e1b34d001cc853a7340/nvdcve/CVE-2009-5020.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2009/AVE-2009-0016.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2009-0005","file_name":"2009/AVE-2009-0005.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2009-1151","title":"phpMyAdmin 配置文件静态代码注入漏洞","description":"phpMyAdmin 的 /config/config.inc.php 配置文件中存在静态代码注入漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过 setup.php 页面的 save 操作向配置文件写入任意 PHP 代码，进而获得远程代码执行权限。该漏洞影响 phpMyAdmin 2.11.x 系列早于 2.11.9.5 版本及 3.x 系列早于 3.1.3.1 版本，CVSS 评分 9.8，危害等级严重。由于无需认证即可利用且存在公开的 Metasploit 利用模块，实际攻击风险极高。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.8,"aliases":["CVE-2009-1151"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2009-03-26","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"立即升级 phpMyAdmin 至 2.11.9.5 或 3.1.3.1 及以上版本；删除或限制访问 /setup/ 目录，在 Web 服务器配置中添加访问控制规则禁止外部访问 setup.php；禁用 config 目录的写入权限；如无法升级，可临时移除 config/config.inc.php 文件并设置 $cfg['SetupDisable'] = true。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.phpmyadmin.net/home_page/security/PMASA-2009-3.php","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/8921","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/16913","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/34236","http://www.debian.org/security/2009/dsa-1824","http://security.gentoo.org/glsa/glsa-200906-03.xml","http://lists.opensuse.org/opensuse-security-announce/2009-04/msg00003.html","http://secunia.com/advisories/34430","http://secunia.com/advisories/34642","http://secunia.com/advisories/35585","http://secunia.com/advisories/35635","http://www.mandriva.com/security/advisories?name=MDVSA-2009:115","http://www.gnucitizen.org/blog/cve-2009-1151-phpmyadmin-remote-code-execution-proof-of-concept/","http://labs.neohapsis.com/2009/04/06/about-cve-2009-1151/","https://www.cisa.gov/known-exploited-vulnerabilities-catalog?field_cve=CVE-2009-1151"],"poc_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/8921"],"exp_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/16913"],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2009/AVE-2009-0005.toml"}]